  RISK SCANNING DESIGN NOTES:
    dependency scanner: dependency-check CLI (must be in PATH)
    invocation:         --project project --scan <path> --format JSON --out <tmpdir>
    image scanner:      trivy CLI (must be in PATH)
    invocation:         image --format json --quiet -o <tmpfile> <imageRef>
    both runners:       spawnSync, temp file/dir cleanup in finally
    error shape:        { ok: false, engine, error: string } — never throws
    suppression match:  fingerprint first, then file+ruleId pair
    severity mapping:   CVSS-based (mapSeverityFromCvss) or string normalisation

